        				<p></p>
        				<div id="articleSubmissionTypes">
        					<ul>
        						<li><a href="/submission-guidelines/preparing-your-manuscript/marine-record">Marine Record</a></li>
        						<li><a href="/submission-guidelines/preparing-your-manuscript/research">Research</a></li>
        						<li><a href="/submission-guidelines/preparing-your-manuscript/review">Review</a></li>
        					</ul>
        				</div>
        				<p></p>
        				<p>Click the relevant link to find style and formatting information for the article you are going to submit.</p>
        			</div>
        		</div>
        	</li>
        	<li class="c-list-group__item">
        		General formatting rules for all article types - <a href="/submission-guidelines/preparing-your-manuscript"> Preparing your manuscript </a>
        	</li>
        	<li class="c-list-group__item">
        		Make sure your submission is complete - <a href="/submission-guidelines/prepare-supporting-information"> Prepare supporting information </a>
        	</li>
        	<li class="c-list-group__item">
        		Copyright and license agreement - <a href="/submission-guidelines/conditions-of-publication"> Conditions of publication </a>
        	</li>
        	<li class="c-list-group__item">
        		Read and agree to our Editorial Policies - <a href="http://www.biomedcentral.com/getpublished/editorial-policies"> Editorial policies </a>
        	</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</li>
<li class="c-steps__item">
